PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX cc: <http://creativecommons.org/ns#>

PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX onto: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX yago: <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?volcano ?elevation WHERE {
  ?volcano a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Volcano> .
  ?volcano <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/locatedInArea> ?area .
  ?area <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Countries_in_Africa> .
  
  OPTIONAL { ?volcano <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/elevation> ?elevation1 . }
  OPTIONAL { ?volcano <http://dbpedia.org/property/elevationM> ?elevation2 . }
  
  BIND(COALESCE(?elevation1, ?elevation2) AS ?elevation)
  
  FILTER(BOUND(?elevation))
}
ORDER BY DESC(?elevation)
LIMIT 1

generated_query:
PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
PREFIX cc: <http://creativecommons.org/ns#>
PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
PREFIX ontolex: <http://www.w3.org/ns/lemon/ontolex#>
PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
PREFIX prov: <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#>
PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dbpedia2: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX onto: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbr: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX yago: <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?label WHERE {
  ?ship a <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Ship> .
  ?ship <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:Christopher_Columbus> .
  ?ship <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> ?label .
  FILTER (lang(?label) = "en")
  FILTER (?label IN ("Santa María", "Pinta", "Niña"))
}
